notes:
- The game cannot be launched from within the application;
- If a new game is installed after Vortex, it'll be unable to manage mods for that game until the symlinks are rebuild;
- Games installed outside of $HOME/.steam/steam, $HOME/.local/share/Steam or $HOME/.local/share/lutris/runners/winesteam require manual configuration of the scripts
- Vortex must be installed in the same drive as the games

input_menu.description:
MANUAL STEPS REQUIRED:

 Vortex is tested and guaranteed to have basic functionality working with the version supplied in this installer. Updates have been shown to break things very often.

 In order to keep Vortex from updating automatically, please follow these steps:
 1. Disconnect from the internet NOW to keep Vortex from updating on its first launch;
 2. After the first launch, go to 'Settings > Vortex > Update' and select the option 'No automatic updates';
 3. Close Vortex and reconnect to the internet;
